        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR6t0288-start">
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:16:08.561+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_31-35.p2.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b09-h.15">Uji (Being-Time, or the Identity of Being and Time)</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T09:53:12.76+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s1">A high monk1 once said:</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T09:53:16.954+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s2">"The uji is standing on the top of a mountain,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T09:53:19.693+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s3">going to the bottom of the deep sea;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T09:53:21.71+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s4">[Acala2 with] three heads and eight arms,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T09:53:24.015+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s9" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s5">[the Buddha-body of] eight3 or sixteen feet4;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T09:53:28.729+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s11" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s6">a shujō5 and a hossu6,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T09:53:30.436+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s13" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s7">a round pillar and a garden lantern,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T09:53:33.785+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s15" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s8">ordinary people;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T09:53:36.243+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s17" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s9">and the earth and the sky"</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T09:54:02.97+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s9a">The "uji"</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T09:54:03.879+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s10">means that time is being</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:10:43.597+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p1.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s11">and vice versa.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:10:45.667+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s12">The Buddha-body of sixteen feet is time.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:10:49.415+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p2.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s14">it has a glorious function of time.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:10:52.161+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p2.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s15">About this we must study the twenty-four hours of today.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:10:47.327+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p2.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s13">Therefore,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:15:44.998+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s16">[Acala with] three heads and eight arms is also time.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:16:16.352+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p3.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s17">Therefore,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:16:21.159+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p3.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s18">he is identical with the twenty-four hours of today.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:16:37.429+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s19">Indeed we have never measured the length of the hours,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:16:38.272+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p4.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s20">but we call them such.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:17:03.707+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p4.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s21">...</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:17:35.693+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s22">The passing traces [of things] are so clear</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:17:37.245+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p5.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s23">that no one has ever doubted them.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:17:53.977+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p5.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s24">However,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:17:54.867+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p5.s9" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s25">this does not mean that they know them well.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:18:43.408+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p6.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s26">Originally, ordinary people</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:18:50.457+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p6.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s27">did not always doubt unknown things or matters,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:33:20.38+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p6.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s28">so their future doubt</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:33:21.307+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p6.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s29">is not always consistent</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:33:24.346+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p6.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s30">with their present one.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:33:37.964+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p6.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s31">[For this reason] doubt itself</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:33:38.993+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p7.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s32">is only a provisional aspect of time.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:42:20.543+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s33">We regard ourselves as the whole universe.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:42:29.099+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s34">Therefore, we should regard each thing in whole world</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:42:29.879+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p1.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s35">as its provisional aspect of time.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:42:45.82+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s36">Each thing does not  hinder others</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:42:46.572+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p2.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s37">any more than each time does.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:43:05.185+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s38">Therefore,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:44:12.257+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p3.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s39">we are awakened to the bodhi-mind,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:44:15.047+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p3.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s40">train ourselves and</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:44:18.301+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s41">become enlightened,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:45:08.725+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s42">identically and simultaneously</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:45:09.725+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s43">with the whole universe.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:45:56.523+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s44">In short, we regard  ourselves as such.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:45:57.398+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p6.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s45">Such is the fact that we ourselves</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:45:58.514+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p6.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s46">are time.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:59:22.458+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s47">For this reason,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:59:33.573+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s48">we must realize that there are various things in the whole world</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T10:59:55.353+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p1.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s49">and that each of them is in [identical with] the whole world.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:00:26.269+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s50">To realize this one-whole</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:00:26.957+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p2.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s51">is the starting point of Buddhist training.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:00:35.695+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s52">As soon as we have reached this realm,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:01:24.082+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p3.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s53">we shall find that each thing is always such</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:01:25.276+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p3.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s54">whether we can understand it or not.</seg>
                    <span old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s55"/>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:01:36.382+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s56">Therefore,each time is the whole.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:01:52.98+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p4.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s57">All things and phenomena are time.</seg>
                    <span old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s58"/>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:03:57.547+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s59">Each time</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:04:01.948+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p6.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s60">is the whole being and the world.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:04:23.446+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p6.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s61">Let us just try to see or think</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:04:24.519+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p6.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s62">if there is the whole being or the world apart from the present time.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:06:16.649+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-h" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c11-h.18">Sansui-kyo (Mountains and Water in Buddhism)</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:11:39.16+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s1">Mountains and water [before us] now</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:11:40.38+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s2">are the appearance of the Law of ancient high monks.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:13:01.905+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s3">Mountains are nothing but mountains;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:13:02.768+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p2.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s4">water is nothing but water</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:13:11.014+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s5">From time immemorial both of them are ultimate reality,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:13:16.445+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p3.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s6">so they have their own free function now;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:13:43.038+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s7">they are also original,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:13:49.877+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p4.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s8">and so are beyond actuality.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:14:20.033+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s9">A mountain has great functions</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:14:25.273+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p5.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s10">[that give rise to clouds or the wind].</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:14:47.069+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p5.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s11">By studying this we never fail</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:14:48.101+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p6.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s12">to realize the free function</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:14:50.151+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p6.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s13">of going on clouds and with the wind.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:20:18.258+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-02.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s13.1">Abbot Tao-kai1 of Mount Ta-yang said to some monks,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:20:19.912+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-02.p1.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s14">"A blue mountain always walks.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:20:21.089+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-02.p1.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s15">A sterile maiden has a baby at night."</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:21:17.608+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s16">A mountain has its own function fully.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:21:18.673+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s17">...</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:21:20.714+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s18">Therefore it is always stable</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:21:21.987+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p2.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s19">and walks.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:21:38.195+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s20">We must study</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:21:38.603+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p3.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s21">this walk carefully.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:22:06.158+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s22">Ordinarily, we may think it walks</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:22:07.443+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p4.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s23">like a man's,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:22:09.021+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p4.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s24">but we must not doubt this only</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:22:11.88+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p4.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s25">because it does not look so.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:22:33.926+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s26">His statement</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:22:38.948+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s27">already shows us that [a mountain] walks.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:23:26.511+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p1.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s28">This is the essence of the walk of the mountain.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:23:34.611+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s29">We must clarify his words "...always walks"</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:23:56.893+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s30">A mountain walks, so it is always stable.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:24:33.269+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s31">It walks much faster</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:24:34.344+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p4.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s32">than the wind,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:24:36.71+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p4.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s33">but a man on the mountain</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:24:39.701+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p4.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s34">is ignorant [of this fact].</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:27:47.426+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s35">Because a mountain is [nothing but a mountain]</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:27:47.988+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p5.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s36">just as when blossoms open the whole world becomes spring-like.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:28:34.394+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p6.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s37">The same can also be said</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:28:35.698+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p6.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s38">of a man outside the mountain.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:29:03.546+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p7.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s39">[Because his world is nothing but his world.]  For this reason, those who have no eye for this mountain</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:29:11.832+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p7.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s40">cannot realize, know,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:29:12.72+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p7.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s41">see or hear this fact.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:32:29.505+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p8.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s42">Those who doubt the walk of a mountain</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:32:39.499+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p8.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s43">would be unaware of, and blind to, their own walk,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:32:42.07+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p9.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s44">though really they walk themselves.</seg>
                    <span old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s45"/>
                    <span old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s46"/>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:34:15.458+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p10.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s48">On the contrary, however, those who realize their own walk</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:34:10.928+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p10.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s49">will unfailingly grasp that of a blue mountain.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:34:59.657+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s50">The blue mountain is no more sentient</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:35:00.731+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s51">or insentient being</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:35:02.516+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s52">than ourselves.</seg>
                    <span old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s53"/>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:35:58.486+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s54">Now we cannot doubt the walk of a blue mountain,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:35:59.356+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s55">nor can we tell how fare it walks.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:38:15.053+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p4.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s56">We should carefully examine various kinds of walk</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:38:16.294+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s57">- the constantly free advance and retreat from time immemorial -</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:38:36.126+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p5.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s58">of a blue mountain and of our own.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:42:26.985+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-06.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s66">If the various kinds of walk stop,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:42:32.652+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-06.p1.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s67">no Buddhas and patriarchs will appear in the world.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:42:41.83+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-06.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s68">If they had come to an end,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:42:42.458+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-06.p2.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s69">the Law would not be transmitted now.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:43:04.794+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-06.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s70">[A blue mountain] is always going ahead</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:43:05.88+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-06.p3.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s71">and back.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:43:26.595+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-06.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s72">But its going-ahead</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:43:27.283+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-06.p4.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s73">is not for or against its going-back,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:43:33.707+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-06.p4.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s74">and vice versa.</seg>
                    <span old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s75"/>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:43:55.09+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-06.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s76">We regard this function as the flowing of a mountain</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:43:56.146+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-06.p5.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s77">or a flowing mountain.<!-- inserted here --></seg>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
